  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will evaluate the feasibility, toxicity, and efficacy of docetaxel/estramustine,
      as in the adjuvant therapy of patients with high-risk prostate cancer after definitive local
      therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Upon determination of eligibility, patients will receive:

      Docetaxel + Estramustine
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
